Dialogue: 0,00:00:55.35,00:00:58.64,Default,,0,0,0,,We lost 300 ryo, thanks \Nto your meddling.
Dialogue: 0,00:00:58.81,00:01:01.44,Default,,0,0,0,,We won't go back empty-handed.
Dialogue: 0,00:01:01.60,00:01:04.90,Default,,0,0,0,,If your hands are so \Nempty, will you hold this?
Dialogue: 0,00:01:33.18,00:01:36.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it true they hired you \Nfor only twenty ryo?
Dialogue: 0,00:01:36.43,00:01:37.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,00:01:38.18,00:01:42.27,Default,,0,0,0,,The sword we stole was a treasure \Ngiven to them by the Shogun.
Dialogue: 0,00:01:42.39,00:01:46.40,Default,,0,0,0,,And they'll only pay \Ntwenty to get it back?
Dialogue: 0,00:01:48.36,00:01:49.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Ridiculous!
Dialogue: 0,00:01:49.44,00:01:51.74,Default,,0,0,0,,They're a poor, small clan.
Dialogue: 0,00:01:51.86,00:01:55.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Trying to swindle 300 ryo for \Na sword is asking too much.
Dialogue: 0,00:01:57.32,00:01:59.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up! Damn you!
Dialogue: 0,00:02:02.83,00:02:05.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Looks like a nasty \Nstorm's brewing...
Dialogue: 0,00:02:05.37,00:02:07.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Can't waste my time here!
Dialogue: 0,00:02:09.34,00:02:14.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Ninja Scroll
Dialogue: 0,00:03:19.87,00:03:21.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I'm sorry for you.
Dialogue: 0,00:03:22.28,00:03:24.16,Default,,0,0,0,,That was one hell of a storm!
Dialogue: 0,00:03:24.16,00:03:27.16,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right! My roof got blown \Noff and scared my wife so bad...
Dialogue: 0,00:03:27.16,00:03:28.96,Default,,0,0,0,,...that she went into labor.
Dialogue: 0,00:03:29.08,00:03:30.63,Default,,0,0,0,,It was really something.
Dialogue: 0,00:03:30.75,00:03:33.00,Default,,0,0,0,,That's your seventh kid, right?
Dialogue: 0,00:03:33.13,00:03:34.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Nope, the ninth.
Dialogue: 0,00:03:34.63,00:03:37.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa! You must really \Nlove your wife!
Dialogue: 0,00:03:39.43,00:03:43.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't that Sakichi's daughter \Nfrom Shimoda Village?
Dialogue: 0,00:03:44.26,00:03:46.22,Default,,0,0,0,,What's with her?
Dialogue: 0,00:03:51.86,00:03:53.23,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?!
Dialogue: 0,00:03:59.28,00:04:01.24,Default,,0,0,0,,All... dead...
Dialogue: 0,00:04:02.53,00:04:05.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Everybody's dead.
Dialogue: 0,00:04:05.66,00:04:07.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Dead?!
Dialogue: 0,00:04:07.58,00:04:11.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Plague... Plague did it...
Dialogue: 0,00:04:17.05,00:04:18.67,Default,,0,0,0,,My god !
Dialogue: 0,00:04:19.13,00:04:22.14,Default,,0,0,0,,This area's off limits! \NNo one goes through!
Dialogue: 0,00:04:22.14,00:04:25.81,Default,,0,0,0,,This road's closed until \Nthe epidemic is over.
Dialogue: 0,00:04:25.97,00:04:28.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Epidemic?! The hell with that!
Dialogue: 0,00:04:30.85,00:04:31.73,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,00:04:31.73,00:04:35.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Sir, my scout saw a \Nstrange group of men
Dialogue: 0,00:04:35.52,00:04:39.70,Default,,0,0,0,,ride toward Shimoda \NVillage late last night.
Dialogue: 0,00:04:40.86,00:04:43.16,Default,,0,0,0,,It might have something \Nto do with this
Dialogue: 0,00:04:43.16,00:04:45.66,Default,,0,0,0,,epidemic so I came to \Ntell you, Chamberlain.
Dialogue: 0,00:04:45.70,00:04:51.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Meaning what? That they spread a plague \Nas they passed through the village?
Dialogue: 0,00:04:51.42,00:04:53.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Ridiculous! Why \Nwould they do that?
Dialogue: 0,00:04:54.71,00:04:56.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Something's fishy.
Dialogue: 0,00:04:56.88,00:04:58.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Let it alone.
Dialogue: 0,00:05:02.43,00:05:04.26,Default,,0,0,0,,On second thought, we can't.
Dialogue: 0,00:05:04.26,00:05:06.76,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the order to \Nall of you Koga ninja.
Dialogue: 0,00:05:06.76,00:05:09.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Go to Shimoda Village and \Nfind what really happened.
Dialogue: 0,00:05:09.98,00:05:10.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Sir!
Dialogue: 0,00:05:10.89,00:05:14.19,Default,,0,0,0,,One more thing. If any of \Nyour people get infected...
Dialogue: 0,00:05:15.23,00:05:16.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Understood, sir.
Dialogue: 0,00:05:17.65,00:05:19.82,Default,,0,0,0,,The first group will follow the \NShirakawa River from the north.
Dialogue: 0,00:05:20.28,00:05:23.20,Default,,0,0,0,,The second will cross \NTaro Pass from the west.
Dialogue: 0,00:05:23.20,00:05:26.20,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll reach Shimoda Village \Nin about an hour. Understand?
Dialogue: 0,00:05:26.74,00:05:30.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Hikoza saw them. There were only eight. \NNo match for us.
Dialogue: 0,00:05:32.16,00:05:33.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Our real enemy is this epidemic.
Dialogue: 0,00:05:35.17,00:05:36.63,Default,,0,0,0,,True.
Dialogue: 0,00:05:47.43,00:05:48.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Kagero...
Dialogue: 0,00:05:56.52,00:05:59.07,Default,,0,0,0,,You intend to leave \Nme behind, Hanza?
Dialogue: 0,00:05:59.82,00:06:02.86,Default,,0,0,0,,You have your own \Nduties, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,00:06:02.86,00:06:06.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Poison tasting is very important. \NDon't forget that.
Dialogue: 0,00:06:06.78,00:06:11.08,Default,,0,0,0,,While our lord is away from his \Ndomain, the work isn't necessary.
Dialogue: 0,00:06:11.08,00:06:13.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Until he returns...
Dialogue: 0,00:06:13.71,00:06:15.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I am one of the Koga ninja!
Dialogue: 0,00:06:16.54,00:06:18.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I cannot take you.
Dialogue: 0,00:06:18.54,00:06:21.09,Default,,0,0,0,,You could all be \Nkilled out there.
Dialogue: 0,00:06:21.09,00:06:25.43,Default,,0,0,0,,How can I just sit and \Nwait here alone?!
Dialogue: 0,00:06:41.73,00:06:45.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Kagero's gotten even \Nmore beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,00:06:45.90,00:06:48.12,Default,,0,0,0,,All the more reason to pity her.
Dialogue: 0,00:06:48.24,00:06:50.70,Default,,0,0,0,,It's her destiny. \NShe must hate it.
Dialogue: 0,00:06:51.33,00:06:54.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Enough. Where are \NHikoza and the others?
Dialogue: 0,00:06:54.33,00:06:57.29,Default,,0,0,0,,They were right behind us. \NI'll have a look.
Dialogue: 0,00:07:12.64,00:07:14.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,00:07:18.52,00:07:20.02,Default,,0,0,0,,What the...?!
Dialogue: 0,00:07:47.22,00:07:48.43,Default,,0,0,0,,There!
Dialogue: 0,00:08:10.28,00:08:11.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Shit!
Dialogue: 0,00:08:21.46,00:08:22.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Tessai!
Dialogue: 0,00:08:27.67,00:08:29.34,Default,,0,0,0,,You are indeed a sorry sight.
Dialogue: 0,00:08:30.93,00:08:32.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Shall we go?
Dialogue: 0,00:08:45.40,00:08:47.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Who was that freak?
Dialogue: 0,00:08:48.82,00:08:51.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Forget it. I don't want \Nto see him again, anyway.
Dialogue: 0,00:08:52.41,00:08:56.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm grateful to you. I am \NKagero of the Koga ninja.
Dialogue: 0,00:08:57.95,00:09:01.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Jubei. Kibagami Jubei.
Dialogue: 0,00:09:02.50,00:09:05.67,Default,,0,0,0,,The town of Kakio is to the west. \NOur paths part here.
Dialogue: 0,00:09:56.18,00:09:57.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, hi...
Dialogue: 0,00:09:59.56,00:10:02.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I know the way now, so...
Dialogue: 0,00:10:05.56,00:10:07.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Ow...
Dialogue: 0,00:10:07.11,00:10:10.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, I got it. Are we done now?
Dialogue: 0,00:10:11.61,00:10:15.03,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no reason we \Nshould kill each other.
Dialogue: 0,00:10:19.33,00:10:21.100,Default,,0,0,0,,If you're not going to end this... \NI will!
Dialogue: 0,00:10:23.08,00:10:24.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Like hell!
Dialogue: 0,00:10:34.22,00:10:38.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Strange skill you have. But \Nit can't hurt my body.
Dialogue: 0,00:10:40.10,00:10:41.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Seems that way.
Dialogue: 0,00:10:55.49,00:10:59.41,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong, Monster? Your \Nskin's starting to crumble!
Dialogue: 0,00:11:02.58,00:11:03.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Die!
Dialogue: 0,00:11:34.98,00:11:37.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Splendid !
Dialogue: 0,00:11:37.11,00:11:40.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Your sword flew swift \Nas the wind itself and
Dialogue: 0,00:11:40.57,00:11:43.91,Default,,0,0,0,,slashed your enemy like \Na cyclone's touch.
Dialogue: 0,00:11:45.20,00:11:48.96,Default,,0,0,0,,He was no match for you. \NWhy don't you join me?
Dialogue: 0,00:11:48.96,00:11:53.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Your skills will be of great help \Nfor me to fight the likes of him.
Dialogue: 0,00:11:54.42,00:11:58.97,Default,,0,0,0,,You're joking. Who'd want to \Nfight a monster like him again?
Dialogue: 0,00:12:00.01,00:12:02.97,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll have to. They \Nwon't leave you alone.
Dialogue: 0,00:12:02.97,00:12:07.06,Default,,0,0,0,,You just killed one of the \NEight Devils of Kimon.
Dialogue: 0,00:12:08.60,00:12:12.61,Default,,0,0,0,,You didn't beat him \Nby yourself, though.
Dialogue: 0,00:12:14.02,00:12:18.53,Default,,0,0,0,,That Koga ninja woman... \NInteresting technique she uses.
Dialogue: 0,00:12:35.30,00:12:39.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Lord Genma. All is \Nproceeding as planned.
Dialogue: 0,00:12:45.05,00:12:49.77,Default,,0,0,0,,It arrives from the Shogun of the \NDark by six tomorrow evening.
Dialogue: 0,00:12:50.98,00:12:55.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Very well. Write \Nto him in return.
Dialogue: 0,00:12:55.94,00:13:01.70,Default,,0,0,0,,"We return in three days. There's \Nnothing to worry about."
Dialogue: 0,00:13:01.70,00:13:03.28,Default,,0,0,0,,At once.
Dialogue: 0,00:13:08.08,00:13:10.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't Tessai back yet?
Dialogue: 0,00:13:10.54,00:13:15.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Benisato went to look for him. \NWe're all alone.
Dialogue: 0,00:13:16.75,00:13:20.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Yurimaru... I've \Nalways loved you.
Dialogue: 0,00:13:29.89,00:13:32.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't push your luck, Zakuro.
Dialogue: 0,00:13:32.52,00:13:35.98,Default,,0,0,0,,You're of no interest to me. \NNow go and stand watch.
Dialogue: 0,00:13:47.33,00:13:49.12,Default,,0,0,0,,So, it's true.
Dialogue: 0,00:13:49.79,00:13:52.87,Default,,0,0,0,,May your dreams be pleasant \Nones in Genma's arms.
Dialogue: 0,00:13:52.87,00:13:57.46,Default,,0,0,0,,However, Yurimaru, Genma makes \Nlove to both men and women.
Dialogue: 0,00:13:57.71,00:14:01.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you know he makes \Nlove to Benisato?
Dialogue: 0,00:14:01.34,00:14:03.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Apparently not.
Dialogue: 0,00:14:52.27,00:14:55.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Where are you headed?
Dialogue: 0,00:14:57.19,00:14:59.86,Default,,0,0,0,,No place in particular. You?
Dialogue: 0,00:15:00.48,00:15:06.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm looking for somebody, and you \Nlook exactly like him, so...
Dialogue: 0,00:15:07.24,00:15:11.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Strangers can look alike. I'm \NKibagami Jubei, a wanderer...
Dialogue: 0,00:15:23.71,00:15:25.55,Default,,0,0,0,,It was most certainly your face.
Dialogue: 0,00:15:25.88,00:15:29.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Tessai was able to make \Nan impression of it.
Dialogue: 0,00:15:46.44,00:15:48.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Just leave me the hell alone!
Dialogue: 0,00:15:57.12,00:15:59.25,Default,,0,0,0,,A cast-off skin.
Dialogue: 0,00:15:59.25,00:16:02.71,Default,,0,0,0,,She shed it like a \Nsnake and escaped.
Dialogue: 0,00:16:04.80,00:16:07.47,Default,,0,0,0,,A gang of freaks, one and all.
Dialogue: 0,00:16:09.68,00:16:14.14,Default,,0,0,0,,You've no obligation. I just \Ndidn't want you to die yet.
Dialogue: 0,00:16:15.10,00:16:17.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Who are these Eight \NDevils of Kimon?
Dialogue: 0,00:16:18.39,00:16:20.56,Default,,0,0,0,,A group of ninja who work \Nfor the Shogun of the Dark.
Dialogue: 0,00:16:20.56,00:16:22.52,Default,,0,0,0,,You know of the \NShogun of the Dark?
Dialogue: 0,00:16:22.19,00:16:25.61,Default,,0,0,0,,He wants to rebuild the Toyotomi \Nclan, the former rulers of Japan.
Dialogue: 0,00:16:25.61,00:16:29.95,Default,,0,0,0,,He has 16 lords behind him and is \Ntrying to expand his influence.
Dialogue: 0,00:16:29.95,00:16:33.12,Default,,0,0,0,,The most dangerous enemy \Nof the Tokugawa Shogunate.
Dialogue: 0,00:16:33.45,00:16:37.58,Default,,0,0,0,,His power is supported in the \Nshadows by the Eight Devils.
Dialogue: 0,00:16:37.58,00:16:40.12,Default,,0,0,0,,What are they up to \Nhere in Mochizuki?
Dialogue: 0,00:16:41.17,00:16:44.50,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what I came here to find out. \NIt's a tough job.
Dialogue: 0,00:16:46.00,00:16:49.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Why don't you work for \Nme, for 100 ryo?
Dialogue: 0,00:16:50.22,00:16:53.14,Default,,0,0,0,,A Tokugawa spy wants \Nto hire a ninja?
Dialogue: 0,00:16:54.80,00:16:57.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm afraid I have no choice. \NIt's an emergency.
Dialogue: 0,00:16:57.31,00:17:00.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Only I managed to make \Nit here to Mochizuki.
Dialogue: 0,00:17:01.02,00:17:03.60,Default,,0,0,0,,The Eight Devils killed everyone \Nelse in my party on our way here.
Dialogue: 0,00:17:03.60,00:17:06.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I need your help by all means!
Dialogue: 0,00:17:07.23,00:17:10.24,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll never get away from them.
Dialogue: 0,00:17:10.24,00:17:12.57,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll have to fight \Nthem sooner or later.
Dialogue: 0,00:17:12.57,00:17:15.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Join me. You can kill two \Nbirds with one stone, right?
Dialogue: 0,00:17:16.37,00:17:20.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't think so. Now why don't \Nyou just leave me alone?
Dialogue: 0,00:17:22.87,00:17:25.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I see. Too bad.
Dialogue: 0,00:17:26.00,00:17:27.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Such a pity...
Dialogue: 0,00:17:30.55,00:17:35.01,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll lose your precious life.
Dialogue: 0,00:17:35.47,00:17:36.60,Default,,0,0,0,,You're stubborn.
Dialogue: 0,00:17:37.10,00:17:40.68,Default,,0,0,0,,No, what I speak of is literally of \Nlife or death importance to you.
Dialogue: 0,00:17:40.68,00:17:45.23,Default,,0,0,0,,You see, that shuriken \Nwas poisoned.
Dialogue: 0,00:17:45.23,00:17:47.77,Default,,0,0,0,,It won't kill you instantly, \Nbut in a day and a
Dialogue: 0,00:17:47.77,00:17:50.57,Default,,0,0,0,,night, when it starts to \Nwork, nothing can stop it.
Dialogue: 0,00:17:52.20,00:17:56.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Unless you get the antidote. \NAnd only I know what it is.
Dialogue: 0,00:17:56.66,00:17:59.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Work for me and I'll tell \Nyou the antidote along
Dialogue: 0,00:17:59.49,00:18:01.95,Default,,0,0,0,,with the hundred ryo \Nwhen the job is done.
Dialogue: 0,00:18:03.12,00:18:05.00,Default,,0,0,0,,You're bluffing.
Dialogue: 0,00:18:10.51,00:18:12.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I speak the truth.
Dialogue: 0,00:18:12.17,00:18:16.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Tell me now. What's \Nthe antidote?
Dialogue: 0,00:18:16.09,00:18:20.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Not until you work for me. Kill \Nme and you've killed yourself!
Dialogue: 0,00:18:26.06,00:18:27.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Now you'll need the \Nantidote for yourself.
Dialogue: 0,00:18:28.48,00:18:31.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Poor boy... You've \Nso much to learn.
Dialogue: 0,00:18:31.44,00:18:34.24,Default,,0,0,0,,That isn't the one that hit you.
Dialogue: 0,00:18:34.95,00:18:37.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I threw THAT one away.
Dialogue: 0,00:18:40.87,00:18:41.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Shit!
Dialogue: 0,00:18:42.75,00:18:47.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Kibagami Jubei... You've lost... \Namateur!
Dialogue: 0,00:18:48.63,00:18:52.05,Default,,0,0,0,,My name is Dakuan. \NHow do you do?
Dialogue: 0,00:18:56.72,00:18:57.72,Default,,0,0,0,,So, Benisato...
Dialogue: 0,00:18:57.72,00:19:02.22,Default,,0,0,0,,This man, Kibagami Jubei, is a \Nremnant of the Shogunate's spies?
Dialogue: 0,00:19:02.85,00:19:04.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Possibly.
Dialogue: 0,00:19:04.18,00:19:06.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Why didn't you kill him?
Dialogue: 0,00:19:06.39,00:19:07.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Someone interfered.
Dialogue: 0,00:19:07.98,00:19:09.23,Default,,0,0,0,,No excuses!
Dialogue: 0,00:19:12.44,00:19:16.57,Default,,0,0,0,,If he's a government spy, \Nhe'll show up here soon.
Dialogue: 0,00:19:16.86,00:19:18.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Be sure to kill him this time.
Dialogue: 0,00:19:19.07,00:19:21.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't need your \Nadvice to do that.
Dialogue: 0,00:19:21.78,00:19:27.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Yurimaru... I'll tell Genma \Nabout this in bed. Do you mind?
Dialogue: 0,00:19:29.75,00:19:30.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Not at all.
Dialogue: 0,00:19:36.30,00:19:37.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Jubei...
Dialogue: 0,00:19:38.26,00:19:42.22,Default,,0,0,0,,There's something \NI've been wondering.
Dialogue: 0,00:19:42.93,00:19:46.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you, by chance, the \Nninja who killed the chief
Dialogue: 0,00:19:46.06,00:19:48.98,Default,,0,0,0,,retainers of the Yamashiro \Nclan five years ago?
Dialogue: 0,00:19:49.90,00:19:53.48,Default,,0,0,0,,He was supposedly a master \Nswordsman, like you.
Dialogue: 0,00:19:56.53,00:19:59.41,Default,,0,0,0,,The retainers had \Ngorged themselves with
Dialogue: 0,00:19:59.41,00:20:02.58,Default,,0,0,0,,gold they secretly dug \Nout of a hidden mine.
Dialogue: 0,00:20:02.83,00:20:06.41,Default,,0,0,0,,The ninja must have killed \Nthem by order of the lord
Dialogue: 0,00:20:06.41,00:20:08.100,Default,,0,0,0,,who wanted to report the \Nmine to the government.
Dialogue: 0,00:20:08.100,00:20:12.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Because if the government found \Nthe hidden gold mine first...
Dialogue: 0,00:20:12.00,00:20:13.92,Default,,0,0,0,,the lord would have \Nlost his fief.
Dialogue: 0,00:20:14.63,00:20:19.18,Default,,0,0,0,,But does that ninja know that after \Nthe retainers were killed...
Dialogue: 0,00:20:19.18,00:20:21.76,Default,,0,0,0,,the government received \Nno report about the mine?
Dialogue: 0,00:20:22.60,00:20:23.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,00:20:23.72,00:20:29.35,Default,,0,0,0,,If a government spy like you knows all \Nthat, then why don't you do something?
Dialogue: 0,00:20:30.10,00:20:35.02,Default,,0,0,0,,No... Even the government can't \Nmove without definite evidence.
Dialogue: 0,00:20:35.02,00:20:38.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Our spies tried many \Ntimes to infiltrate the
Dialogue: 0,00:20:38.15,00:20:41.53,Default,,0,0,0,,clan to find evidence, \Nbut none returned alive.
Dialogue: 0,00:20:41.70,00:20:43.07,Default,,0,0,0,,The Shogun of the Dark...
Dialogue: 0,00:20:43.07,00:20:46.37,Default,,0,0,0,,He stopped them by \Nusing the Kimon ninja.
Dialogue: 0,00:20:47.16,00:20:50.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Why is the Shogun of the Dark \Nhelping the Yamashiro clan?
Dialogue: 0,00:20:51.04,00:20:54.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Simple. He wants the \Ngold mine for himself.
Dialogue: 0,00:20:56.30,00:21:01.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you know how he found the \Nmine before the government?
Dialogue: 0,00:21:01.93,00:21:04.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Somebody gave him \Nthe information.
Dialogue: 0,00:21:04.47,00:21:08.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Somebody who was the leader of \Nthe ninja of the Yamashiro clan.
Dialogue: 0,00:21:09.31,00:21:11.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Himuro... Genma?!
Dialogue: 0,00:21:12.52,00:21:14.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Precisely.
Dialogue: 0,00:21:15.23,00:21:18.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I doubt that. He isn't \Nin this world anymore.
Dialogue: 0,00:21:19.28,00:21:22.78,Default,,0,0,0,,No, he's still very much alive. \NAnd you'll see him soon.
Dialogue: 0,00:21:22.78,00:21:26.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Himuro Genma is the boss \Nof the Kimon monsters.
Dialogue: 0,00:21:26.03,00:21:26.70,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,00:21:27.03,00:21:29.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Shh! Not so loud !
Dialogue: 0,00:21:29.12,00:21:31.16,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't trick me \Nthe same way again!
Dialogue: 0,00:21:31.16,00:21:35.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't be hasty. You'll \Nsoon know the truth.
Dialogue: 0,00:21:35.42,00:21:40.97,Default,,0,0,0,,But you must admit that you \Nand he share a strange fate.
Dialogue: 0,00:21:46.51,00:21:49.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop! You'd kill \Nyour own friend?!
Dialogue: 0,00:21:49.35,00:21:52.81,Default,,0,0,0,,The lord orders it! \NAs did our leader!
Dialogue: 0,00:21:54.31,00:21:55.86,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a trick!
Dialogue: 0,00:21:55.86,00:21:58.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Now that we know the \Ntraitors' secret they want
Dialogue: 0,00:21:58.40,00:22:00.86,Default,,0,0,0,,to get rid of us by making \Nus kill each other.
Dialogue: 0,00:22:01.28,00:22:05.16,Default,,0,0,0,,This is a trap for all of us. \NShinkuro, believe me!
Dialogue: 0,00:22:06.20,00:22:07.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Jubei... Forgive me.
Dialogue: 0,00:22:08.24,00:22:09.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Shinkuro!
Dialogue: 0,00:22:10.41,00:22:11.75,Default,,0,0,0,,His word...
Dialogue: 0,00:22:12.16,00:22:13.16,Default,,0,0,0,,...is law!
Dialogue: 0,00:22:52.45,00:22:57.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I avenged Shinkuro and the others myself. \NGenma can't be alive.
Dialogue: 0,00:22:59.00,00:23:03.05,Default,,0,0,0,,We're getting close. This place \Nis thick with ghosts and blood.
Dialogue: 0,00:23:03.21,00:23:05.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Beyond lies Hell itself.
Dialogue: 0,00:23:09.93,00:23:13.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Heaven must have sent \Nthis mist to help us.
Dialogue: 0,00:23:29.12,00:23:30.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,00:23:38.50,00:23:40.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Double damned mist!
Dialogue: 0,00:24:04.19,00:24:07.70,Default,,0,0,0,,How could he have \Ndodged Shijima's claw?
Dialogue: 0,00:24:36.06,00:24:37.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,00:24:37.18,00:24:40.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard a voice \Nchanting the sutra.
Dialogue: 0,00:24:40.94,00:24:44.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I was praying for \Nthe dead villagers.
Dialogue: 0,00:24:45.15,00:24:48.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you know an epidemic \Nplagues this village?
Dialogue: 0,00:24:50.45,00:24:55.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Poor soul! You'll never \Nleave this village alive.
Dialogue: 0,00:24:55.53,00:24:59.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Here now, let us go to the \Nland of Buddha together.
Dialogue: 0,00:25:05.17,00:25:08.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Have you seen a \Ntraveling monk here?
Dialogue: 0,00:25:09.76,00:25:14.85,Default,,0,0,0,,He'll meet Buddha soon enough. \NI'll send him there.
Dialogue: 0,00:25:15.64,00:25:17.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Such a benevolent nun...
Dialogue: 0,00:25:25.77,00:25:27.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Shit! Another cast-off skin!
Dialogue: 0,00:25:38.20,00:25:42.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Gone... He uses a \Nstrange technique...
Dialogue: 0,00:25:52.84,00:25:55.05,Default,,0,0,0,,As do you. Very strange indeed !
Dialogue: 0,00:26:04.27,00:26:11.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Answer me. Are there any others \Nwith you besides the monk?
Dialogue: 0,00:26:11.94,00:26:15.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course. And not \Njust ten or twenty.
Dialogue: 0,00:26:15.45,00:26:18.70,Default,,0,0,0,,You can send a snake for \Neach and it won't be enough.
Dialogue: 0,00:26:20.29,00:26:21.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Liar!
Dialogue: 0,00:26:22.12,00:26:24.92,Default,,0,0,0,,All right! I'll \Ntell you the truth.
Dialogue: 0,00:26:26.00,00:26:29.71,Default,,0,0,0,,There's two. One's the traveling monk. \NThe other...
Dialogue: 0,00:26:29.84,00:26:31.17,Default,,0,0,0,,...is right behind you.
Dialogue: 0,00:26:33.63,00:26:36.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Lose the snakes. Down \Nto the last one!
Dialogue: 0,00:26:42.68,00:26:43.93,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll be dead soon.
Dialogue: 0,00:26:48.48,00:26:49.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Get rid of them!
Dialogue: 0,00:27:07.96,00:27:10.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Now it's your turn to answer.
Dialogue: 0,00:27:10.29,00:27:13.13,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing in this village? \NTalk!
Dialogue: 0,00:27:34.99,00:27:37.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Twice failed. Unforgivable.
Dialogue: 0,00:27:37.99,00:27:41.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I cast another line onto your \Nneck, but you didn't notice.
Dialogue: 0,00:27:41.99,00:27:44.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Ln the end, just a \Nfoolish amateur.
Dialogue: 0,00:28:03.47,00:28:05.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Idiot! There's still time \Nto suck the poison out!
Dialogue: 0,00:28:06.98,00:28:09.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Poison doesn't work on me. \NMy body's immune to it.
Dialogue: 0,00:28:12.61,00:28:15.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I think I've cleared \Nmy debt to you.
Dialogue: 0,00:28:15.11,00:28:17.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. You saved me.
Dialogue: 0,00:28:18.07,00:28:22.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Your name's Kagero, right? \NWhat are you going to do now?
Dialogue: 0,00:28:22.32,00:28:24.70,Default,,0,0,0,,That's none of your concern.
Dialogue: 0,00:28:25.62,00:28:27.79,Default,,0,0,0,,If it isn't, then what the \Nhell am I doing here?!
Dialogue: 0,00:28:29.16,00:28:31.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I have to discover their plan.
Dialogue: 0,00:28:32.42,00:28:34.63,Default,,0,0,0,,By yourself? Impossible!
Dialogue: 0,00:28:34.63,00:28:36.80,Default,,0,0,0,,They're too strong. \NThink this over.
Dialogue: 0,00:28:37.30,00:28:39.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Stay out of my way.
Dialogue: 0,00:28:39.01,00:28:42.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I've no reason to \Ntake orders from you.
Dialogue: 0,00:28:45.85,00:28:48.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold a moment, Kunoichi of Koga.
Dialogue: 0,00:28:48.27,00:28:53.19,Default,,0,0,0,,My name is Dakuan. Why \Ndon't you join me?
Dialogue: 0,00:28:53.19,00:28:56.98,Default,,0,0,0,,This man is my \Ntrustworthy assistant.
Dialogue: 0,00:28:57.48,00:28:59.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I wasn't planning on \Nhelping a government spy.
Dialogue: 0,00:28:59.99,00:29:02.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, quit complaining !
Dialogue: 0,00:29:02.28,00:29:03.53,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you say, woman?
Dialogue: 0,00:29:03.74,00:29:08.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Our aims may differ, but we \Nthree share a common enemy.
Dialogue: 0,00:29:08.20,00:29:11.17,Default,,0,0,0,,And three is mightier than one.
Dialogue: 0,00:29:11.17,00:29:14.59,Default,,0,0,0,,And I happen to have some \Ninformation you don't know.
Dialogue: 0,00:29:14.59,00:29:17.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Such as who is giving \Nthem their orders.
Dialogue: 0,00:29:17.63,00:29:19.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll tell you on the way.
Dialogue: 0,00:29:23.72,00:29:24.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I need no friends.
Dialogue: 0,00:29:25.47,00:29:29.35,Default,,0,0,0,,But I may need your information.
Dialogue: 0,00:29:29.35,00:29:30.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Very well.
Dialogue: 0,00:29:37.07,00:29:41.74,Default,,0,0,0,,My, she's a lovely, sexy \Nlittle thing, isn't she!
Dialogue: 0,00:29:42.20,00:29:45.03,Default,,0,0,0,,What's running through that \Ntwisted skull of yours?
Dialogue: 0,00:29:45.49,00:29:49.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Well now, that Kunoichi \Ncould prove very useful.
Dialogue: 0,00:29:49.24,00:29:53.04,Default,,0,0,0,,She has a technique to poison \Nthe man she sleeps with.
Dialogue: 0,00:29:53.58,00:29:58.38,Default,,0,0,0,,The big guy you killed had \Nbeen poisoned by her.
Dialogue: 0,00:30:04.13,00:30:07.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyone who makes \Nlove to her dies.
Dialogue: 0,00:30:07.05,00:30:11.68,Default,,0,0,0,,A perfect woman for \Nthis hellish world.
Dialogue: 0,00:30:53.68,00:30:56.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Your skill is as \Nmarvelous as ever.
Dialogue: 0,00:30:56.40,00:30:59.82,Default,,0,0,0,,No... He was able to kill a \Nmighty ninja like Tessai.
Dialogue: 0,00:30:59.82,00:31:03.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't be off guard. It's \Npossible he got away.
Dialogue: 0,00:31:04.44,00:31:06.70,Default,,0,0,0,,The four of you \Nwill check it out.
Dialogue: 0,00:31:06.70,00:31:08.87,Default,,0,0,0,,You're a cautious one, Yurimaru.
Dialogue: 0,00:31:09.03,00:31:14.12,Default,,0,0,0,,We have an important mission. \NWe take every precaution.
Dialogue: 0,00:31:14.25,00:31:16.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I know, I know. Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,00:31:16.75,00:31:18.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Then go.
Dialogue: 0,00:31:21.09,00:31:25.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Yurimaru, Benisato's death... \NHow fortunate for you!
Dialogue: 0,00:31:34.89,00:31:37.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Only things he killed \Nwere the fish.
Dialogue: 0,00:31:37.10,00:31:39.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Good. Otherwise we \Nwouldn't get our chance.
Dialogue: 0,00:31:39.65,00:31:41.90,Default,,0,0,0,,It's getting quite \Ninteresting, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,00:31:56.71,00:31:59.88,Default,,0,0,0,,How is it? Just as we thought?
Dialogue: 0,00:32:00.83,00:32:03.75,Default,,0,0,0,,They poisoned the wells \Nand killed the villagers.
Dialogue: 0,00:32:03.75,00:32:05.84,Default,,0,0,0,,And then blamed it on plague.
Dialogue: 0,00:32:06.51,00:32:09.76,Default,,0,0,0,,A trick to keep the \Nvillagers away.
Dialogue: 0,00:32:10.64,00:32:15.43,Default,,0,0,0,,They're planning something... \Nquite extraordinary.
Dialogue: 0,00:32:26.28,00:32:28.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd like to know what it is.
Dialogue: 0,00:32:29.32,00:32:32.37,Default,,0,0,0,,That's fine, just don't get \Nyourself involved too deeply.
Dialogue: 0,00:32:32.37,00:32:34.08,Default,,0,0,0,,It could prove fatal.
Dialogue: 0,00:32:55.72,00:32:57.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I see. Guide the others.
Dialogue: 0,00:33:15.70,00:33:16.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Run for it!
Dialogue: 0,00:33:39.02,00:33:40.98,Default,,0,0,0,,We can't outrun them.
Dialogue: 0,00:33:42.85,00:33:44.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Kagero...
Dialogue: 0,00:34:02.41,00:34:05.04,Default,,0,0,0,,So, the pollen is mixed \Nwith a sleeping potion.
Dialogue: 0,00:34:05.04,00:34:06.96,Default,,0,0,0,,But how long will \Nit hold them back?
Dialogue: 0,00:34:08.04,00:34:09.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Why, you!
Dialogue: 0,00:34:10.21,00:34:11.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Girl!
Dialogue: 0,00:34:11.42,00:34:13.76,Default,,0,0,0,,You have to hold them off \Ntill Jubei kills him!
Dialogue: 0,00:34:13.76,00:34:15.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Do whatever it takes!
Dialogue: 0,00:34:29.98,00:34:31.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Call off your bees!
Dialogue: 0,00:34:32.86,00:34:35.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm afraid you must \Nbeat me first.
Dialogue: 0,00:34:37.45,00:34:39.58,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't know anything, do you?
Dialogue: 0,00:34:39.58,00:34:42.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you think I ran in \Nhere to escape you?
Dialogue: 0,00:34:43.08,00:34:44.08,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I don't.
Dialogue: 0,00:34:44.08,00:34:46.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I have lots of questions for \Nyou, but no time to ask them.
Dialogue: 0,00:34:47.08,00:34:50.84,Default,,0,0,0,,No, just one thing. Tell \Nme, is Himuro Genma alive?
Dialogue: 0,00:34:51.00,00:34:52.71,Default,,0,0,0,,So what if he is?
Dialogue: 0,00:34:52.71,00:34:55.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I ask because I sent \Nhim to Hell before.
Dialogue: 0,00:34:55.51,00:34:58.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that so? Then I'll \Nhave to be careful.
Dialogue: 0,00:34:58.30,00:35:02.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Unlike Genma, I don't have the \Ntechnique to reincarnate myself.
Dialogue: 0,00:35:03.10,00:35:04.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Reincarnation?
Dialogue: 0,00:35:13.15,00:35:15.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Fool! You've damaged the hive!
Dialogue: 0,00:35:32.34,00:35:35.09,Default,,0,0,0,,The second you come up for \Nair is the second you die!
Dialogue: 0,00:35:37.97,00:35:41.22,Default,,0,0,0,,He's mine! Keep \Nyour hands off him!
Dialogue: 0,00:35:41.51,00:35:43.27,Default,,0,0,0,,What about the \NKunoichi and the monk?
Dialogue: 0,00:35:43.27,00:35:47.06,Default,,0,0,0,,My bees should finish \Nthem off soon.
Dialogue: 0,00:35:56.57,00:36:00.28,Default,,0,0,0,,How far is he trying to run? \NWhat a poor loser!
Dialogue: 0,00:36:15.13,00:36:17.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you think he's fallen \Nvictim to the throat needle?
Dialogue: 0,00:36:28.60,00:36:33.23,Default,,0,0,0,,No... The bees in the hive are \Ntrying to escape the water.
Dialogue: 0,00:36:33.23,00:36:37.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Desperately stinging his body as \Nthey do so... Mushizo's lost.
Dialogue: 0,00:36:49.25,00:36:51.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Took his time about it, but \Nhe finally killed him.
Dialogue: 0,00:37:06.22,00:37:11.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Reincarnation? Did he mean Himuro \NGenma's come back to life?
Dialogue: 0,00:37:12.85,00:37:14.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Impossible!
Dialogue: 0,00:37:27.54,00:37:31.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Reincarnation? I've heard \Nabout the technique.
Dialogue: 0,00:37:32.58,00:37:37.84,Default,,0,0,0,,You must control your flesh and \Nblood down to the tiniest bones.
Dialogue: 0,00:37:37.96,00:37:43.76,Default,,0,0,0,,If your limbs or even your head were \Ncut off, you'd be able to rejoin them.
Dialogue: 0,00:37:44.26,00:37:47.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Reincarnation... That's a \Ntechnique of immortality.
Dialogue: 0,00:37:47.47,00:37:49.60,Default,,0,0,0,,It can never be achieved \Nby a human being.
Dialogue: 0,00:37:50.02,00:37:52.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, well... That's \Na hell of a trick!
Dialogue: 0,00:37:52.73,00:37:57.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway, the Kimon monsters \Nare now all after you.
Dialogue: 0,00:37:57.19,00:37:59.48,Default,,0,0,0,,That means I can move easily.
Dialogue: 0,00:38:02.45,00:38:04.86,Default,,0,0,0,,If you're lucky, \Nwe'll meet again.
Dialogue: 0,00:38:07.74,00:38:10.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Why did you join him?
Dialogue: 0,00:38:10.70,00:38:13.87,Default,,0,0,0,,He hired me... For 100 ryo.
Dialogue: 0,00:38:14.08,00:38:16.96,Default,,0,0,0,,You're a mercenary ninja? One \Nwho'd do anything for money?
Dialogue: 0,00:38:17.84,00:38:19.71,Default,,0,0,0,,You could say that.
Dialogue: 0,00:38:19.71,00:38:23.76,Default,,0,0,0,,But he suckered me into it. \NTrapped me.
Dialogue: 0,00:38:24.38,00:38:27.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll die of his \Npoison in half a day.
Dialogue: 0,00:38:28.51,00:38:32.35,Default,,0,0,0,,He promised me an antidote \Nalong with the gold.
Dialogue: 0,00:38:32.35,00:38:36.48,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why I work for him. \NI can't back out now.
Dialogue: 0,00:38:36.81,00:38:39.90,Default,,0,0,0,,You'd better run for it while \NI divert their attention.
Dialogue: 0,00:38:40.57,00:38:43.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't do that. I'd \Nowe you another debt.
Dialogue: 0,00:38:44.20,00:38:45.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Forget about any debts.
Dialogue: 0,00:38:45.70,00:38:49.08,Default,,0,0,0,,And I told you I don't have \Nto take orders from you.
Dialogue: 0,00:38:49.08,00:38:51.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Besides, I'm ready \Nto die any moment.
Dialogue: 0,00:38:51.70,00:38:53.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Relax. Stop pretending \Nyou're so tough.
Dialogue: 0,00:38:53.66,00:38:54.91,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,00:38:56.37,00:38:58.71,Default,,0,0,0,,It's this humid weather!
Dialogue: 0,00:38:58.71,00:39:03.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I wish a storm would come and \Ncool off that hot head of yours.
Dialogue: 0,00:39:07.34,00:39:09.39,Default,,0,0,0,,You're in no position \Nto worry about me.
Dialogue: 0,00:39:15.94,00:39:17.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Storm...
Dialogue: 0,00:39:19.23,00:39:23.44,Default,,0,0,0,,They came on the night \Nof that big storm...
Dialogue: 0,00:39:28.03,00:39:30.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, where can I get a \Ngood look at this area?
Dialogue: 0,00:39:37.50,00:39:38.88,Default,,0,0,0,,How about there?
Dialogue: 0,00:39:38.88,00:39:40.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing.
Dialogue: 0,00:39:40.13,00:39:41.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Keep looking !
Dialogue: 0,00:39:54.77,00:39:55.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Hanza...
Dialogue: 0,00:39:55.77,00:39:56.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,00:39:57.56,00:39:58.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Hanza!
Dialogue: 0,00:40:03.23,00:40:05.90,Default,,0,0,0,,There's a cliff in front of you! \NStop!
Dialogue: 0,00:40:06.86,00:40:07.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn!
Dialogue: 0,00:40:21.96,00:40:23.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Gotcha!
Dialogue: 0,00:40:23.09,00:40:23.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Shit!
Dialogue: 0,00:40:32.01,00:40:36.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Fool! They got you so soon? \NWe still had a lot to do.
Dialogue: 0,00:40:41.60,00:40:44.61,Default,,0,0,0,,The scent of blasted flesh, \Ngrilled to perfection...
Dialogue: 0,00:40:44.61,00:40:46.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Such a lovely smell.
Dialogue: 0,00:41:11.26,00:41:12.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't... move...
Dialogue: 0,00:41:12.93,00:41:15.10,Default,,0,0,0,,That's enough. Let me go.
Dialogue: 0,00:41:15.10,00:41:17.14,Default,,0,0,0,,It's my fault I fell \Nfor their trap.
Dialogue: 0,00:41:17.52,00:41:19.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up! Don't talk!
Dialogue: 0,00:41:20.19,00:41:22.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Let go of me! I don't \Nwant your help.
Dialogue: 0,00:41:22.81,00:41:24.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,00:41:32.57,00:41:35.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Go on, grab it!
Dialogue: 0,00:41:47.75,00:41:50.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Just gonna hang onto me all day?
Dialogue: 0,00:42:07.61,00:42:12.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I am Utsutsu Mujuro. I've been \Nlonging to challenge you.
Dialogue: 0,00:42:18.99,00:42:21.41,Default,,0,0,0,,He's here for me. Stay here.
Dialogue: 0,00:42:34.26,00:42:38.60,Default,,0,0,0,,You lured me here because I'm blind? \NIs that your plan?
Dialogue: 0,00:42:53.07,00:42:55.66,Default,,0,0,0,,If you want to kill me, \Nthen don't make a sound.
Dialogue: 0,00:42:56.82,00:43:00.66,Default,,0,0,0,,That's impossible. But maybe I can \Nturn your skill to my advantage.
Dialogue: 0,00:43:39.74,00:43:41.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I told you to stay back!
Dialogue: 0,00:43:48.17,00:43:50.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Your sight is your weakness.
Dialogue: 0,00:43:54.09,00:43:54.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Outta the way!
Dialogue: 0,00:44:07.44,00:44:08.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Impossible...
Dialogue: 0,00:44:31.79,00:44:35.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Would you give it a rest?! What \Nthe hell were you thinking?!
Dialogue: 0,00:44:36.30,00:44:38.17,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you so obsessed about?
Dialogue: 0,00:44:38.51,00:44:42.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up! You're the one obsessed \Nwith repaying me for saving you!
Dialogue: 0,00:44:42.93,00:44:45.89,Default,,0,0,0,,You act like you've got \Nsome kind of death wish!
Dialogue: 0,00:44:46.97,00:44:48.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it because of your body?
Dialogue: 0,00:44:52.36,00:44:56.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it true the men you sleep \Nwith die from the poison?
Dialogue: 0,00:45:02.03,00:45:03.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Embrace me and you'll find out.
Dialogue: 0,00:45:09.75,00:45:10.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Idiot!
Dialogue: 0,00:45:11.37,00:45:14.00,Default,,0,0,0,,My body is saturated \Nwith poison.
Dialogue: 0,00:45:14.00,00:45:17.92,Default,,0,0,0,,It's so strong that a touch of \Nmy lips will kill instantly.
Dialogue: 0,00:45:19.01,00:45:24.39,Default,,0,0,0,,No one can touch me. Anyone \Nwho dares to... dies.
Dialogue: 0,00:45:24.97,00:45:27.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Did the poison twist \Nyour heart, too?
Dialogue: 0,00:45:27.64,00:45:29.27,Default,,0,0,0,,How dare you!
Dialogue: 0,00:45:35.61,00:45:38.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I hate people who don't \Nvalue their own lives.
Dialogue: 0,00:45:57.30,00:46:01.01,Default,,0,0,0,,You've no idea... You \Ncouldn't understand !
Dialogue: 0,00:46:41.71,00:46:45.01,Default,,0,0,0,,The cargo from the ship that ran \Naground in the storm two days ago.
Dialogue: 0,00:46:45.01,00:46:47.14,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what they're after.
Dialogue: 0,00:46:47.14,00:46:50.47,Default,,0,0,0,,They butchered the villagers \Nlike animals for it.
Dialogue: 0,00:47:04.15,00:47:06.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Where does this road lead?
Dialogue: 0,00:47:12.41,00:47:13.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Chamberlain!
Dialogue: 0,00:47:14.33,00:47:15.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Lord Hyobu, is it true?
Dialogue: 0,00:47:15.75,00:47:21.30,Default,,0,0,0,,That the Koga ninja who went to investigate \NShimoda Village were wiped out?
Dialogue: 0,00:47:21.55,00:47:22.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Exactly.
Dialogue: 0,00:47:22.88,00:47:26.72,Default,,0,0,0,,But how?! This is an emergency.
Dialogue: 0,00:47:26.72,00:47:29.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll take my men to the \Nvillage immediately.
Dialogue: 0,00:47:29.18,00:47:30.35,Default,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,00:47:30.35,00:47:33.56,Default,,0,0,0,,If this is serious \Nenough to jeopardize the
Dialogue: 0,00:47:33.56,00:47:37.10,Default,,0,0,0,,safety of our clan, we \Nmust move very carefully.
Dialogue: 0,00:47:37.85,00:47:40.27,Default,,0,0,0,,That's how small clans \Nlike ours survive.
Dialogue: 0,00:47:40.27,00:47:41.32,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,00:47:41.65,00:47:45.11,Default,,0,0,0,,The Kunoichi who survived is \Ncontinuing the investigation.
Dialogue: 0,00:47:45.24,00:47:47.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait for her report.
Dialogue: 0,00:48:01.21,00:48:03.38,Default,,0,0,0,,You're tired from being \Nso tense all the time.
Dialogue: 0,00:48:03.38,00:48:04.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Get some more sleep.
Dialogue: 0,00:48:56.97,00:49:00.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Those wheel tracks lead \Nto Kashima Harbor.
Dialogue: 0,00:49:00.77,00:49:03.31,Default,,0,0,0,,They're probably going to \Ntransport the cargo out by boat.
Dialogue: 0,00:49:03.65,00:49:04.19,Default,,0,0,0,,If I don't stop them...
Dialogue: 0,00:49:04.19,00:49:08.11,Default,,0,0,0,,those dead villagers and the Koga \Nninja will never rest in peace.
Dialogue: 0,00:49:10.78,00:49:14.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll cooperate with you \Ntill the mission's over.
Dialogue: 0,00:49:14.08,00:49:18.04,Default,,0,0,0,,But if you insult me again, \NI'll kill you where you stand !
Dialogue: 0,00:49:33.43,00:49:37.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen well, you who labor \Nfor the Shogun of the Dark.
Dialogue: 0,00:49:37.47,00:49:41.02,Default,,0,0,0,,This mission could very \Nwell decide our fate!
Dialogue: 0,00:49:41.31,00:49:44.40,Default,,0,0,0,,This ship will reach \NMochizuki in a few hours.
Dialogue: 0,00:49:44.40,00:49:47.53,Default,,0,0,0,,We must retrieve the \Ncargo at any cost!
Dialogue: 0,00:49:47.82,00:49:50.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Understood? At any cost!
Dialogue: 0,00:50:09.92,00:50:12.51,Default,,0,0,0,,The towns must have cleared out \Nout of fear of the epidemic.
Dialogue: 0,00:50:13.34,00:50:16.26,Default,,0,0,0,,One horse was enough to \Nscare them all away.
Dialogue: 0,00:50:20.98,00:50:24.19,Default,,0,0,0,,So, you're still alive. \NI've been worried.
Dialogue: 0,00:50:24.98,00:50:27.19,Default,,0,0,0,,It's nice to see you, too.
Dialogue: 0,00:50:27.44,00:50:30.74,Default,,0,0,0,,They're waiting for a boat \Nto transport the cargo.
Dialogue: 0,00:50:31.28,00:50:33.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you check what the cargo is?
Dialogue: 0,00:50:33.36,00:50:38.12,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I couldn't reach it. But \NI can guess what it is.
Dialogue: 0,00:50:38.12,00:50:40.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Actually, I guessed before \NI came to Mochizuki.
Dialogue: 0,00:50:40.75,00:50:41.75,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,00:50:41.75,00:50:43.87,Default,,0,0,0,,You haven't figured it out?
Dialogue: 0,00:50:43.100,00:50:46.42,Default,,0,0,0,,It's something that has \Nto do with your past.
Dialogue: 0,00:50:47.33,00:50:49.34,Default,,0,0,0,,It's gold, boy.
Dialogue: 0,00:50:49.34,00:50:53.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Gold produced from that \Nsecret Yamashiro mine.
Dialogue: 0,00:50:54.97,00:50:57.14,Default,,0,0,0,,The ship ran aground \Nduring the storm...
Dialogue: 0,00:50:57.14,00:51:01.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Probably on its way to the Shogun \Nof the Dark with caskets of gold.
Dialogue: 0,00:51:01.47,00:51:05.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Gold that's probably been \Nhidden for the last five years.
Dialogue: 0,00:51:06.06,00:51:08.27,Default,,0,0,0,,If it reaches his hands,
Dialogue: 0,00:51:08.27,00:51:10.94,Default,,0,0,0,,he'll be powerful enough to \Ntopple the Tokugawa government...
Dialogue: 0,00:51:10.94,00:51:13.11,Default,,0,0,0,,...and plunge the country \Ninto another civil war.
Dialogue: 0,00:51:13.32,00:51:15.36,Default,,0,0,0,,We have to stop it at any cost!
Dialogue: 0,00:51:19.78,00:51:22.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Dakuan, you've got a tail.
Dialogue: 0,00:51:22.41,00:51:23.16,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,00:51:33.71,00:51:35.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Kunoichi, what are you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,00:51:35.93,00:51:39.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm calling a Koga ninja \Nbird that's in this village.
Dialogue: 0,00:51:39.97,00:51:41.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Calling a bird? What for?
Dialogue: 0,00:51:41.93,00:51:44.52,Default,,0,0,0,,It'll carry my message to \Nthe castle chamberlain.
Dialogue: 0,00:51:44.77,00:51:46.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I've discovered \Nwhat they're after.
Dialogue: 0,00:51:46.77,00:51:50.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Ln two hours, his army \Nwill surround the town.
Dialogue: 0,00:51:50.98,00:51:52.57,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not as easy as you think.
Dialogue: 0,00:51:52.90,00:51:56.03,Default,,0,0,0,,The Mochizuki clan will probably \Nignore this whole thing.
Dialogue: 0,00:51:56.49,00:51:57.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?!
Dialogue: 0,00:52:01.78,00:52:03.62,Default,,0,0,0,,The future of the \Nclan is at stake.
Dialogue: 0,00:52:03.62,00:52:06.71,Default,,0,0,0,,This is a power struggle between the \NTokugawa and the Shogun of the Dark.
Dialogue: 0,00:52:06.71,00:52:10.92,Default,,0,0,0,,If a small clan like the Mochizuki \Ngot involved, it'd be smashed !
Dialogue: 0,00:52:14.05,00:52:17.59,Default,,0,0,0,,See nothing, hear nothing. That's \Nthe best course for the clan.
Dialogue: 0,00:52:29.31,00:52:31.86,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll find out soon whether or \Nnot the Mochizuki will move.
Dialogue: 0,00:52:41.82,00:52:43.95,Default,,0,0,0,,So, now what are you playing at?
Dialogue: 0,00:52:44.16,00:52:48.25,Default,,0,0,0,,The man you hired is going \Nto die from your poison.
Dialogue: 0,00:52:48.62,00:52:50.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Tell me how to save him.
Dialogue: 0,00:52:50.71,00:52:55.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Amazing ! You've fallen in \Nlove with Jubei, haven't you?
Dialogue: 0,00:52:57.21,00:53:01.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Fool! I'm only doing it to \Nclear my debt with him!
Dialogue: 0,00:53:01.05,00:53:03.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't think so.
Dialogue: 0,00:53:04.31,00:53:07.77,Default,,0,0,0,,A Kunoichi falling in love! \NWhat's the point?
Dialogue: 0,00:53:10.56,00:53:13.31,Default,,0,0,0,,If you kill me, there'll \Nbe no saving him.
Dialogue: 0,00:53:13.44,00:53:17.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, and your mission \Nwill be a failure.
Dialogue: 0,00:53:33.33,00:53:34.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Shit!
Dialogue: 0,00:53:35.21,00:53:35.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh-oh!
Dialogue: 0,00:53:37.13,00:53:41.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Calm down! That's the \Nreal cure for him.
Dialogue: 0,00:53:41.18,00:53:43.76,Default,,0,0,0,,If you want to save his \Nlife, there's no other way.
Dialogue: 0,00:53:44.01,00:53:46.22,Default,,0,0,0,,It's up to you.
Dialogue: 0,00:54:13.17,00:54:14.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Kunoichi in Custody
Dialogue: 0,00:54:14.38,00:54:19.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Kunoichi in Custody It must have \Nhappened when I went off for a moment.
Dialogue: 0,00:54:19.13,00:54:20.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Kunoichi in Custody
Dialogue: 0,00:54:20.46,00:54:23.43,Default,,0,0,0,,She's most likely dead.
Dialogue: 0,00:54:24.30,00:54:27.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, we've got work to do.
Dialogue: 0,00:54:27.35,00:54:29.81,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll get no help from \Nthe Mochizuki clan.
Dialogue: 0,00:54:33.39,00:54:35.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't fall for their trap.
Dialogue: 0,00:54:36.19,00:54:37.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,00:54:38.36,00:54:40.94,Default,,0,0,0,,What if their ship comes \Nwhile you're at it?
Dialogue: 0,00:54:40.94,00:54:44.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Let her alone! A dead Kunoichi \Nisn't that important!
Dialogue: 0,00:54:45.45,00:54:47.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Not important compared \Nto the great mission?
Dialogue: 0,00:54:47.32,00:54:49.33,Default,,0,0,0,,You're as much of a \Nmonster as they are!
Dialogue: 0,00:54:49.33,00:54:53.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Fool! When you fight monsters, you \Nbecome one yourself or you can't win!
Dialogue: 0,00:54:55.42,00:54:59.96,Default,,0,0,0,,You damn fool boy! Go ahead ! \NGO TO HELL!
Dialogue: 0,00:54:59.96,00:55:03.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn you... !
Dialogue: 0,00:56:05.03,00:56:05.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,00:56:08.41,00:56:09.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Kagero!
Dialogue: 0,00:56:28.26,00:56:32.14,Default,,0,0,0,,You're hard to kill, but... \NWoman, release his pain.
Dialogue: 0,00:56:55.16,00:56:57.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Kibagami Jubei?
Dialogue: 0,00:56:57.83,00:57:00.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. But we've already \Nkilled them all.
Dialogue: 0,00:57:00.83,00:57:03.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Idiot! They still live.
Dialogue: 0,00:57:04.92,00:57:06.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll kill him, for sure!
Dialogue: 0,00:57:06.34,00:57:10.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Stay where you are. Lure \Nthem there and kill them.
Dialogue: 0,00:57:11.09,00:57:12.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Understand?
Dialogue: 0,00:57:12.34,00:57:12.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,00:57:19.02,00:57:21.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Never would I have \Nimagined to see him here.
Dialogue: 0,00:57:21.69,00:57:24.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I look forward to seeing \Nyou again, Jubei.
Dialogue: 0,00:57:25.98,00:57:27.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Genma!
Dialogue: 0,00:57:32.53,00:57:33.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,00:57:34.78,00:57:38.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Forget it. I take it the castle \Nretainers haven't taken any action?
Dialogue: 0,00:57:40.33,00:57:42.71,Default,,0,0,0,,It's been two hours.
Dialogue: 0,00:57:43.29,00:57:44.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,00:57:48.63,00:57:52.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Why... You knew it was a trap, \Nbut you came to help me.
Dialogue: 0,00:57:52.34,00:57:55.76,Default,,0,0,0,,It was stupid. Why \Nrisk your life for me?
Dialogue: 0,00:57:55.76,00:57:57.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Because I can't just \Ntoss aside my comrade.
Dialogue: 0,00:57:57.85,00:57:58.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Comrade?
Dialogue: 0,00:57:59.31,00:58:03.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. We've saved each other \Nover and over since yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,00:58:03.48,00:58:04.86,Default,,0,0,0,,You're a precious friend to me.
Dialogue: 0,00:58:14.11,00:58:14.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Stay!
Dialogue: 0,00:58:15.41,00:58:18.04,Default,,0,0,0,,The Mochizuki clan is \Nstaying out of this one.
Dialogue: 0,00:58:18.04,00:58:19.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Your mission is over.
Dialogue: 0,00:58:20.25,00:58:23.62,Default,,0,0,0,,No, it isn't. I'm \Nstill in debt to you.
Dialogue: 0,00:58:25.38,00:58:26.96,Default,,0,0,0,,You can pay it back later.
Dialogue: 0,00:58:27.84,00:58:30.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Not if you're dead !
Dialogue: 0,00:58:30.17,00:58:31.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll repay it here!
Dialogue: 0,00:58:42.02,00:58:43.73,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,00:58:49.90,00:58:53.36,Default,,0,0,0,,The old man told me how \Nto counteract the poison.
Dialogue: 0,00:58:54.66,00:58:56.45,Default,,0,0,0,,"Kill poison with poison."
Dialogue: 0,00:58:56.82,00:59:01.12,Default,,0,0,0,,He said if you make love to a \Npoison-taster like me, you'll be cured.
Dialogue: 0,00:59:03.79,00:59:05.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Take me...
Dialogue: 0,01:00:00.64,01:00:03.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?! You'll die if you don't!
Dialogue: 0,01:00:03.97,01:00:06.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Why? JUBEI !
Dialogue: 0,01:00:36.97,01:00:39.80,Default,,0,0,0,,We've been waiting ! Load \Nthe ship immediately!
Dialogue: 0,01:01:06.62,01:01:09.92,Default,,0,0,0,,You! Well, I warned \Nyou, didn't I?
Dialogue: 0,01:01:09.92,01:01:13.17,Default,,0,0,0,,We've lost. We'll never \Nbeat that many men.
Dialogue: 0,01:01:13.67,01:01:17.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't intend to let them go. \NWe'll make our stand soon.
Dialogue: 0,01:01:18.63,01:01:19.88,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you planning?
Dialogue: 0,01:01:20.05,01:01:22.89,Default,,0,0,0,,When they finish \Nloading the gold...
Dialogue: 0,01:01:22.89,01:01:24.81,Default,,0,0,0,,...go to the tower \Nand ring the bell.
Dialogue: 0,01:01:25.10,01:01:28.31,Default,,0,0,0,,While they're distracted, \NI'll sneak onboard the ship.
Dialogue: 0,01:01:28.56,01:01:31.44,Default,,0,0,0,,When we're out at sea, \Nwe won't need any storm.
Dialogue: 0,01:01:31.44,01:01:33.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll sink it myself.
Dialogue: 0,01:01:33.31,01:01:34.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Very well.
Dialogue: 0,01:01:35.07,01:01:38.78,Default,,0,0,0,,By the way, did you make \Nlove to that Kunoichi?
Dialogue: 0,01:01:40.32,01:01:44.24,Default,,0,0,0,,None of your damn business! \NNow get going !
Dialogue: 0,01:02:06.47,01:02:09.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Genma... Where are you?
Dialogue: 0,01:02:09.31,01:02:12.56,Default,,0,0,0,,When I die, I'll take \Nyou to hell with me!
Dialogue: 0,01:02:44.76,01:02:47.22,Default,,0,0,0,,The Mochizuki clan?! They're \Nmoving against them!
Dialogue: 0,01:02:52.64,01:02:54.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, Kunoichi! You've \Ndone a fine job.
Dialogue: 0,01:02:55.15,01:02:57.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry, before they get away! \NWhere are the others?
Dialogue: 0,01:02:58.69,01:03:01.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry. They've got \Nthis place surrounded.
Dialogue: 0,01:03:02.07,01:03:03.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Then hurry!
Dialogue: 0,01:03:22.34,01:03:24.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Jubei...
Dialogue: 0,01:03:32.18,01:03:33.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Kagero!
Dialogue: 0,01:03:35.31,01:03:36.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop! It's a trap!
Dialogue: 0,01:03:37.44,01:03:41.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Fool! Sakaki Hyobu \Ndied two days ago.
Dialogue: 0,01:03:55.83,01:03:57.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I killed him personally.
Dialogue: 0,01:03:58.17,01:04:00.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Genma!
Dialogue: 0,01:04:27.90,01:04:31.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Sir, please get aboard \Nthe ship quickly.
Dialogue: 0,01:04:31.32,01:04:34.91,Default,,0,0,0,,The retainers of the Shogun \Nof the Dark are waiting.
Dialogue: 0,01:04:35.75,01:04:39.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Leave Jubei to me. Upon my \Nhonor, I will not fail.
Dialogue: 0,01:04:40.92,01:04:44.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Please grant me this one wish.
Dialogue: 0,01:04:48.55,01:04:50.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Very well then. Go.
Dialogue: 0,01:05:18.33,01:05:22.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Stay out of this. Don't shame me \Nany more than you already have.
Dialogue: 0,01:05:24.79,01:05:26.42,Default,,0,0,0,,So, you are Genma?
Dialogue: 0,01:05:26.96,01:05:30.47,Default,,0,0,0,,The Mochizuki clan \Nsuspects nothing, correct?
Dialogue: 0,01:05:30.47,01:05:32.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. All is well.
Dialogue: 0,01:05:32.47,01:05:36.89,Default,,0,0,0,,You've done a splendid job. I \Nadmire you Devils of Kimon.
Dialogue: 0,01:05:36.97,01:05:40.02,Default,,0,0,0,,The Shogun of the \NDark will be pleased.
Dialogue: 0,01:06:13.18,01:06:15.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Writhe in pain before you die.
Dialogue: 0,01:06:51.17,01:06:54.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Yurimaru seems to have \Nsuffered some ill fortune!
Dialogue: 0,01:06:54.18,01:06:57.55,Default,,0,0,0,,How careless of him to \Nhave fallen into my trap.
Dialogue: 0,01:06:59.01,01:07:01.47,Default,,0,0,0,,It was your own fault, Yurimaru.
Dialogue: 0,01:07:05.23,01:07:06.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,01:07:09.36,01:07:10.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Kagero!
Dialogue: 0,01:07:20.20,01:07:22.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Hang on! Kagero!
Dialogue: 0,01:07:26.25,01:07:27.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Jubei...
Dialogue: 0,01:07:28.04,01:07:29.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I told you not to come.
Dialogue: 0,01:07:30.84,01:07:34.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I wanted... to apologize...
Dialogue: 0,01:07:38.05,01:07:40.47,Default,,0,0,0,,It was the first time...
Dialogue: 0,01:07:40.47,01:07:44.23,Default,,0,0,0,,You didn't treat me like \Nsome poison-taster...
Dialogue: 0,01:07:44.23,01:07:47.40,Default,,0,0,0,,...but like a normal woman.
Dialogue: 0,01:07:48.73,01:07:52.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I knew I was becoming attracted \Nto you, and I was afraid.
Dialogue: 0,01:07:52.40,01:07:56.57,Default,,0,0,0,,So I tried to push you away. \NForgive me...
Dialogue: 0,01:07:59.28,01:08:02.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't care what \Nyou think of me!
Dialogue: 0,01:08:03.100,01:08:08.58,Default,,0,0,0,,If for an antidote... or out of pity... \NI don't care...
Dialogue: 0,01:08:09.29,01:08:12.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I just wish... that \Nyou'd made love to me.
Dialogue: 0,01:08:19.72,01:08:24.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I was stupid... and weak.
Dialogue: 0,01:08:24.10,01:08:27.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Why couldn't I have \Nbeen more honest?
Dialogue: 0,01:08:27.60,01:08:31.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Enough. Don't say any more!
Dialogue: 0,01:09:19.86,01:09:25.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Jubei... I'm glad... \NI met you...
Dialogue: 0,01:10:59.92,01:11:05.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Genma, with the gold's help our \Ndream will soon be reality.
Dialogue: 0,01:11:05.55,01:11:06.59,Default,,0,0,0,,"Our" dream?
Dialogue: 0,01:11:06.59,01:11:12.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Our great dream to topple the Shogunate \Nand restore the reign of the Toyotomi.
Dialogue: 0,01:11:12.73,01:11:14.64,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't understand...
Dialogue: 0,01:11:14.64,01:11:18.23,Default,,0,0,0,,How we, the former retainers \Nof Toyotomi, have suffered.
Dialogue: 0,01:11:18.56,01:11:22.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Now it'll be the Tokugawa who \Nsuffer the agony and torment.
Dialogue: 0,01:11:22.15,01:11:27.95,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll use the gold to buy advanced weapons \Nfrom Spain and defeat the Tokugawa.
Dialogue: 0,01:11:27.95,01:11:32.45,Default,,0,0,0,,That is the dream of all of us who \Nwork for the Shogun of the Dark.
Dialogue: 0,01:11:33.29,01:11:34.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Nonsense.
Dialogue: 0,01:11:36.17,01:11:37.42,Default,,0,0,0,,What did you say?!
Dialogue: 0,01:11:37.63,01:11:39.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I said nonsense.
Dialogue: 0,01:11:39.38,01:11:42.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold your tongue! \NYou're a mere ninja!
Dialogue: 0,01:11:42.46,01:11:44.42,Default,,0,0,0,,My dream is different.
Dialogue: 0,01:11:44.42,01:11:47.39,Default,,0,0,0,,The gold isn't going to \Nthe Shogun of the Dark.
Dialogue: 0,01:11:47.39,01:11:48.14,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,01:11:48.14,01:11:50.35,Default,,0,0,0,,We, the Devils of Kimon, \Nwill take the gold.
Dialogue: 0,01:11:50.47,01:11:52.02,Default,,0,0,0,,You impudent... !
Dialogue: 0,01:11:54.02,01:11:58.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll use it to organize the most \Npowerful army of ninja ever.
Dialogue: 0,01:11:58.35,01:12:02.98,Default,,0,0,0,,And we'll rule the country with \Nterror and power from the shadows.
Dialogue: 0,01:12:03.28,01:12:06.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyone who opposes me, \NTokugawa or Toyotomi...
Dialogue: 0,01:12:06.24,01:12:09.28,Default,,0,0,0,,...even the Shogun of the \NDark himself, shall die.
Dialogue: 0,01:12:10.70,01:12:14.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Meaning the true Shogun of the Dark... \Nwill be me.
Dialogue: 0,01:12:32.35,01:12:38.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Well now, you're here! I was \Njust wishing you'd come.
Dialogue: 0,01:12:38.19,01:12:39.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm glad to hear that.
Dialogue: 0,01:12:39.77,01:12:41.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course.
Dialogue: 0,01:12:41.44,01:12:46.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Without your help, sinking a big \Nship like this would be impossible!
Dialogue: 0,01:12:53.33,01:12:54.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Pathetic old fool!
Dialogue: 0,01:12:56.04,01:12:56.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Over here.
Dialogue: 0,01:13:07.59,01:13:08.55,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,01:13:09.38,01:13:12.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Fire in the hold ! \NWe're gonna sink!
Dialogue: 0,01:13:12.55,01:13:14.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Idiot! Put out the fire!
Dialogue: 0,01:13:14.39,01:13:16.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Impossible! It's a sea of flame!
Dialogue: 0,01:13:16.60,01:13:19.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Put it out! Fight it!
Dialogue: 0,01:13:19.35,01:13:21.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Move it! Move it!
Dialogue: 0,01:13:21.73,01:13:23.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Forget it! Run!
Dialogue: 0,01:13:32.12,01:13:32.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Master Genma!
Dialogue: 0,01:13:34.03,01:13:35.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Pass this message to everyone:
Dialogue: 0,01:13:35.62,01:13:40.79,Default,,0,0,0,,"Abandon ship and hide yourselves. \NI'll call for you someday."
Dialogue: 0,01:13:40.79,01:13:41.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Go.
Dialogue: 0,01:14:21.41,01:14:22.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Genma!
Dialogue: 0,01:14:24.67,01:14:27.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I see you brought back some \Ndevils from your trip to Hell.
Dialogue: 0,01:14:36.76,01:14:38.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Kibagami Jubei...
Dialogue: 0,01:14:38.72,01:14:42.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I should've finished \Nyou with my own hands.
Dialogue: 0,01:14:42.35,01:14:45.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop your whining. \NIt's too late.
Dialogue: 0,01:14:46.90,01:14:50.40,Default,,0,0,0,,You want to avenge \Nthe Kunoichi Kagero?
Dialogue: 0,01:14:50.61,01:14:53.82,Default,,0,0,0,,She was trash in comparison \Nto what I've lost.
Dialogue: 0,01:14:57.87,01:14:59.62,Default,,0,0,0,,You alone I can't forgive!
Dialogue: 0,01:15:53.26,01:15:56.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't kill you yet. Not \Nbefore I make you suffer.
Dialogue: 0,01:15:56.93,01:15:59.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll make you pay for \Nsmashing my dream.
Dialogue: 0,01:15:59.39,01:16:04.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Your dream? That you were going to \Nbe the true Shogun of the Dark?
Dialogue: 0,01:16:05.14,01:16:06.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't make me laugh.
Dialogue: 0,01:16:07.10,01:16:12.15,Default,,0,0,0,,If you became shogun, you'd \Nmake this a world of devils.
Dialogue: 0,01:16:12.82,01:16:17.57,Default,,0,0,0,,If you enjoy their company so much... \Nthen go back to hell!
Dialogue: 0,01:16:34.80,01:16:36.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll kill you!
Dialogue: 0,01:16:39.72,01:16:41.80,Default,,0,0,0,,No one can kill me.
Dialogue: 0,01:16:46.23,01:16:49.10,Default,,0,0,0,,You of all people \Nshould know by now...
Dialogue: 0,01:16:52.02,01:16:54.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I am immortal.
Dialogue: 0,01:16:58.03,01:16:59.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,01:17:14.84,01:17:18.34,Default,,0,0,0,,If you keep coming \Nback to life...
Dialogue: 0,01:17:18.88,01:17:22.64,Default,,0,0,0,,...then I'll kill you as \Nmany times as it takes!
Dialogue: 0,01:18:34.50,01:18:36.04,Default,,0,0,0,,You fool!
Dialogue: 0,01:19:25.18,01:19:28.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Genma! HERE YOU DIE!
Dialogue: 0,01:20:26.70,01:20:28.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Jubei!
Dialogue: 0,01:20:28.07,01:20:32.45,Default,,0,0,0,,You seem to be rid of the \Npoison, thanks to Kagero.
Dialogue: 0,01:20:32.62,01:20:37.04,Default,,0,0,0,,The combination of a poison-tasting \NKunoichi and a talented lone wolf
Dialogue: 0,01:20:37.04,01:20:39.38,Default,,0,0,0,,worked out even better \Nthan I had planned.
Dialogue: 0,01:20:39.58,01:20:40.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Go away.
Dialogue: 0,01:20:45.55,01:20:50.26,Default,,0,0,0,,By the way, I'm sorry about losing Kagero. \NA real pity, that!
Dialogue: 0,01:20:50.34,01:20:53.60,Default,,0,0,0,,But for a scant few \Nmoments, she was able to
Dialogue: 0,01:20:53.60,01:20:56.77,Default,,0,0,0,,be an ordinary girl and \Nmake love with you.
Dialogue: 0,01:20:57.60,01:20:59.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Was that part of your plan, too?
Dialogue: 0,01:20:59.60,01:21:04.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Exactly. To read and control peoples' \Nhearts is the true secret of the ninja.
Dialogue: 0,01:21:06.44,01:21:11.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Still, only true sincerity \Ncan move the human heart.
Dialogue: 0,01:21:11.07,01:21:13.95,Default,,0,0,0,,A twisted old bastard \Nlike me couldn't do it.
Dialogue: 0,01:21:14.08,01:21:17.83,Default,,0,0,0,,You're a hell of a guy. \NI really admire you.
Dialogue: 0,01:21:17.83,01:21:20.83,Default,,0,0,0,,As promised, I'll be waiting \Nin Edo with your 100 ryo.
Dialogue: 0,01:21:20.83,01:21:22.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Come and get it, if \Nyou're still alive.
Dialogue: 0,01:21:29.59,01:21:33.10,Default,,0,0,0,,That makes us even. Now \Nnever cross my path again.
Dialogue: 0,01:21:34.10,01:21:37.81,Default,,0,0,0,,You've beaten me. I thought I'd \Nshut your mouth in Edo, but...
Dialogue: 0,01:21:37.81,01:21:41.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Still, in your condition you likely \Nwon't even make it to the shore.
Dialogue: 0,01:21:41.85,01:21:44.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Everything will end \Njust as I planned.
Dialogue: 0,01:22:30.57,01:22:35.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Come with me, let's go \Nout to see the stars
Dialogue: 0,01:22:37.08,01:22:42.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Evening has only just begun
Dialogue: 0,01:22:43.08,01:22:55.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want anything, only for you to \Nbe at my side, a smile on your face
Dialogue: 0,01:22:55.97,01:23:00.68,Default,,0,0,0,,A distant summer, the \Ntwo of us alone...
Dialogue: 0,01:23:02.52,01:23:07.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Sitting on the beach \Nwe used to walk
Dialogue: 0,01:23:08.44,01:23:19.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Trying to retrieve the \Ngentleness that we left behind
Dialogue: 0,01:23:21.08,01:23:27.58,Default,,0,0,0,,A distant ballad sung \Nto no one at all...
Dialogue: 0,01:23:27.58,01:23:32.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I can still hear it even now
Dialogue: 0,01:23:33.97,01:23:45.94,Default,,0,0,0,,It embraces my wandering heart \Njust like the cool night wind
Dialogue: 0,01:24:11.88,01:24:23.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Looking at you, only you saying \Nthings hard for us to say
Dialogue: 0,01:24:24.43,01:24:35.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Times may have changed, but I know my \Nfeelings are still the same for you
Dialogue: 0,01:24:37.11,01:24:43.54,Default,,0,0,0,,A distant ballad sung \Nto no one at all...
Dialogue: 0,01:24:43.54,01:24:48.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I can still hear it even now
Dialogue: 0,01:24:49.58,01:25:03.60,Default,,0,0,0,,It embraces my wandering heart \Njust like the cool night wind
